{"tid":1765872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"殺害示威者罪成　伊拉克警員被判死刑","createTime":"2019-12-02T07:45:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T17:12:37.000Z","uid":109780,"like":134,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"3a6bd60ec083061ef8dd39f64621262975aeef8f","tid":1765872,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T07:45:19.000Z","msg":"伊拉克反政府示威從10月至今已持續兩個月，當局以實彈鎮壓，造成數百人死亡。國會昨日（ 12 月1日）接受總理邁赫迪（Adil Abdul-Mahdi）請辭。另外，當地一名警員殺害示威者罪刑成立，被判處死刑，為近兩個月來首次有警員因殺害示威者被定罪。<br />\n<br />\n法新社報道，伊拉克法院裁定2名警員11月2日在南部城市參與殺死7名示威者，分別被判處絞刑及監禁7年。<br />\n<br />\n伊拉克反政府示威持續2個月，雖然總理邁赫迪請辭，惟伊拉克首都巴格達（Baghdad）、南部城市納傑夫（Najaf）近日仍有示威。保安部隊以發射實彈及催淚彈驅散人群，至少3人死亡、58人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AE%BA%E5%AE%B3%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E4%BC%8A%E6%8B%89%E5%85%8B%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%A4%E6%AD%BB%E5%88%91/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E4%25BC%258A%25E6%258B%2589%25E5%2585%258B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2588%25A4%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%2588%2591%2F&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0WjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=02214e8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E4%25BC%258A%25E6%258B%2589%25E5%2585%258B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2588%25A4%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%2588%2591%2F&h=8d9cec18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AE%BA%E5%AE%B3%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E4%BC%8A%E6%8B%89%E5%85%8B%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%A4%E6%AD%BB%E5%88%91/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港幾時有呢一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b6f1e185120e02d5081c82bb